  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Bristol is served on a half board basis with breakfast and dinner taken in the hotels restaurant.</p>
<p>Breakfast consists of a continental buffet with hot and cold options.</p>
<p>Dinner includes a four course fixed evening meal.</p>
<p>A Christmas and New Year gala dinner are included.</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
